        <mxCell id="combine" value="🧩  Put it all together&#xa;The AI combines everything&#xa;the helpers found and&#xa;writes one helpful reply." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#CFD8E3;strokeColor=#4A6E8C;strokeWidth=2;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=13;fontColor=#2E4A66" vertex="1" parent="1">
